additionalInformation: The aftertreatment ECU has severely limited the operation of the truck as a result of active faults with the aftertreament system.  Do not troubleshoot this fault code since it originates from other fault codes.
comments: Do not troubleshoot this DTC since it originates from another active DTC.
dtcDescription: A vehicle speed limitation is active as a result of one or more active faults in the emission control system.

guidanceList.possibleCause: P1514 - Emission control system detected a DEF dosing fault.
